## Environment Variables needed

DATABASE_URL=        # Neon PostgreSQL connection string
JWT_SECRET=          # Long random string for signing JWTs
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL= # e.g. http://localhost:3000

## Setup Commands
```bash
bun install
bunx prisma generate
bunx prisma db push
bun run dev
```